query:
UPDATE inventory i
JOIN warehouseLocations wl ON i.locationId = wl.id
SET i.tenantId = (SELECT id FROM tenants WHERE name LIKE '%Albert Einstein%' LIMIT 1)
WHERE wl.code LIKE 'Z01-01-%';
